= Twisted Web =

Twisted web is a web server, and also provides basic HTTP client support. You may want to check out [http://divmod.org/projects/nevow Nevow], a templating toolkit designed for twisted.web, and [wiki:TwistedWeb2 Twisted Web2], the next generation Twisted web server.

Twisted Web is available under the MIT Free Software licence.


= Download =
 * [http://twistedmatrix.com/projects/web/NEWS.txt Release notes] for Twisted Web 0.5.0
 * Stable: Twisted Web is part of Twisted. Tarballs and Windows installers are at the TwistedProject page.
 * Trunk: svn co svn://svn.twistedmatrix.com/svn/Twisted/trunk Twisted
 * [http://tmrc.mit.edu/mirror/twisted/Web/0.5/TwistedWeb-0.5.0.tar.bz2 Minimal Tarball]. This will require downloading of additional dependencies. We encourage you to use the downloads at TwistedProject, instead of this minimal download.

